# Merging Advertising Data with SQL (CTE & UNION)

## ğŸ“ Project Description / Proje TanÄ±mÄ±
-The goal is to combine advertising data from two different sources (Google Ads and Facebook Ads) using Common Table Expressions (CTE) and UNION ALL.
Projenin amacÄ±, Ortak Tablo Ä°fadeleri (CTE) ve UNION ALL kullanarak Google Ads ve Facebook Ads'ten gelen reklam verilerini birleÅŸtirmektir.

## Objectives / Hedefler
-Merge advertising data from facebook_ads_basic_daily and google_ads_basic_daily using CTE.
CTE kullanarak facebook_ads_basic_daily ve google_ads_basic_daily tablolarÄ±ndaki reklam verilerini birleÅŸtirmek.
-Add a media_source column to identify the origin of the data.
Veri kaynaÄŸÄ±nÄ± belirlemek iÃ§in media_source sÃ¼tunu eklemek.
-Aggregate metrics by ad_date and media_source.
Verileri ad_date (reklam tarihi) ve media_source (medya kaynaÄŸÄ±) sÃ¼tunlarÄ±na gÃ¶re gruplamak.
-Calculate total spend, impressions, clicks, and conversion value for each date and source.
Her tarih ve medya kaynaÄŸÄ± iÃ§in toplam harcama, gÃ¶sterim, tÄ±klama ve dÃ¶nÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼m deÄŸerlerini hesaplamak.

## SQL Query Explanation / SQL Sorgusunun AÃ§Ä±klamasÄ±
-CTE (Common Table Expressions) is used to separate data from Facebook and Google Ads before merging them.
CTE, verileri birleÅŸtirmeden Ã¶nce Facebook ve Google Ads'ten gelen verileri ayrÄ± ayrÄ± almak iÃ§in kullanÄ±lmÄ±ÅŸtÄ±r.
-UNION ALL combines data from both sources into a single dataset.
UNION ALL, her iki kaynaktan gelen verileri tek bir veri setinde birleÅŸtirmek iÃ§in kullanÄ±lmÄ±ÅŸtÄ±r.
-GROUP BY ensures the aggregation of metrics by ad_date and media_source.
GROUP BY kullanÄ±larak, veriler ad_date (tarih) ve media_source (medya kaynaÄŸÄ±) sÃ¼tunlarÄ±na gÃ¶re gruplandÄ±rÄ±lmÄ±ÅŸtÄ±r.
-ORDER BY ad_date sorts the final output in ascending order.
ORDER BY ad_date kullanÄ±larak sonuÃ§lar tarihe gÃ¶re artan sÄ±rayla sÄ±ralanmÄ±ÅŸtÄ±r.

## Technologies Used / KullanÄ±lan Teknolojiler
PostgreSQL
SQL Queries (CTE, UNION ALL, Aggregation)

```sql
WITH facebookCTE AS 
	(SELECT ad_date, 'Facebook' AS media_source, spend, impressions, reach, clicks, leads, value 
	 FROM facebook_ads_basic_daily),
	 googleCTE AS 
	 (SELECT ad_date, 'Google' AS media_source, spend, impressions, reach, clicks, leads, value
	  FROM public.google_ads_basic_daily),
	 mergedCTE AS 
	 (SELECT *
	 FROM facebookCTE
	 UNION ALL 
	 SELECT *
	 FROM googleCTE)
SELECT  ad_date, media_source,
		sum(spend) AS total_spend, 
	    sum(impressions) AS total_impressions, 
	    sum(clicks) AS total_clicks, 
	    sum(value) AS total_value 
FROM mergedCTE
GROUP BY ad_date, media_source
ORDER BY ad_date;
```
